#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:3
msgid "Contributing to sphinxcontrib-rust"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:5
msgid "First off, thanks for taking the time to contribute! ❤️"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:7
msgid "All types of contributions are encouraged and valued."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:9
msgid ""
"See the Contents for different ways to help and details about how this "
"project handles them. Please make sure to read the relevant section before "
"making your contribution. It will make it a lot easier for us maintainers "
"and smooth out the experience for all involved. The community looks forward "
"to your contributions. 🎉"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:13
msgid ""
"And if you like the project, but just don't have time to contribute, that's "
"fine. There are other easy ways to support the project and show your "
"appreciation, which we would also be very happy about:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:16
msgid "Star the project"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:17
msgid "Share it online"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:18
msgid "Refer this project in your project's readme"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:19
msgid "Mention the project at local meetups and tell your friends/colleagues"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:21
msgid "Contents"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:24
msgid "Questions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:26
msgid ""
"Please read the documentation on `readthedocs <https://sphinxcontrib-rust."
"readthedocs.io/en/stable/index.html>`_ or `Gitlab Pages <https://"
"sphinxcontrib-rust-mmc691-8fb22cc6152ca3a233f41dbc6179d6a5fd539.gitlab.io/"
">`_ before asking the question."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:30
msgid ""
"If the documentation does not cover it, search for existing `Issues <https://"
"gitlab.com/munir0b0t/sphinxcontrib-rust/issues>`_ that might help you. In "
"case you have found a suitable issue and still need clarification, you can "
"write your question in this issue."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you then still feel the need to ask a question and need clarification, we "
"recommend the following:"
