msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:38
msgid ""
"Provide the project, Sphinx, Python and Rust versions and also the OS used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:40
msgid "We will then take care of the issue as soon as possible."
